Chef's Salsa Crema Verde
Boil tomatilla's
- Char over open flame or pan sear until darkened
- Char peppers with diced siraches/jalepenos/pepper of choice
Add onions, cilantro (not charred)
Salt and pepper to taste
Optionally add avacados
Blend until smooth

If you want creamy crema, throw sour cream in, or salvadorian crema 
